Package: tidyplots
Title: Tidy Plots Using the Pipe
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jan Broder", "Engler", , "broder.engler@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3169-2076"))
Description: The goal of `tidyplots` is to streamline the creation of publication-ready plots for scientific papers, by making it easy to gradually add and refine plot elements. It allows precise control over composition, style, and absolute sizes, while its utilization of the pipe `%>%` simplifies the construction of advanced plotting pipelines.
